<h2 id="download" style="text-align:center;border-bottom:none;padding-bottom:0">Download Sonic GT</h2>

<strong>Sonic GT</strong> is a complete, free game for <strong>Windows PC</strong> with 4 full zones, a boss final, and all 7 characters playable. Released at SAGE 2020, the download includes everything — no account or registration needed.

<div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;margin:12px auto">
