<div class="details-box">
<h3>How to Install Sonic GT</h3>
<div class="details-grid">
<details>
<summary>Windows</summary>
<p>Download the ZIP file from the link above. Extract all files to any folder using WinRAR or 7-Zip. Run the game executable (.exe) to start playing. A controller is recommended for the best experience. <strong>Tip:</strong> If you use a controller, disconnect it while navigating menus (the game has a known bug with controllers in menus), then reconnect once your level loads.</p>
