The community regularly compares the level design to <strong>"Sonic Adventure 1 expanded tenfold"</strong> — massive playgrounds where high paths reward skilled players with faster routes, while lower paths keep the experience accessible. There are no gimmick-heavy sections or forced 2D segments. Just pure 3D Sonic freedom.

